## Security

- Secrets never in repos - use a secret manager (Cloudflare Workers env vars, AWS Secrets Manager, 1Password, etc.)
- Never track `.env` files - `.gitignore` covers `*.env` and `.env.*` by default in this template
- Never enter credit card numbers, API keys, or credentials in chat
- API keys in messages can leak in transcripts - prefer environment variables

