## CLI Toolset

Tier 1 (installed via `install-cli.ps1`): **rg, fd, bat, fzf, jq, xh, zoxide**.
Prefer these over PowerShell-native equivalents:

- `rg` over `Select-String` (faster, gitignore-aware)
- `fd` over `Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Filter` (faster, smart-case)
- `bat` over `Get-Content` for viewing source (syntax highlight)
- `jq` over `ConvertFrom-Json | Where-Object` for ad-hoc JSON filtering
- `xh` over `Invoke-RestMethod` for REST endpoints
- `z <prefix>` (zoxide) over `cd <full-path>` for hopping between repos

Tier 2 (lazygit, gron, uv, starship, gh-dash) installed by the same script. See [`cli_toolset.md`](cli_toolset.md) for full reference.

